						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">cartlemmy wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Ah yes, actually I guess I use a counter. I like using the counter, because you can use it for things like "Do this every <em>n</em> frames":<br /></div>
<br />
<br />I used to do timing that way, but in most cases it turned out to be really limiting compared to using a fixed-point counter.  With fixed point for example, if you wanted to do something every 2 frames, you would add $80 to the counter every frame, and trigger on carry.  Instead of $80 though you can add any value (zero would stop it) for 256 different speeds.</div>

